Naira Marley goes wild Naira Marley is no doubt a fan favorite. In December, when he put together the fan-appreciative Marlian Fest, the crowd went crazy. As his colleague friends performed their hits, their was massive reaction by way of responses, dance, and fist pumps, head bumps. His (Naira Marley) set was the loudest, as Marlians sang along their Supreme Leader to the high heavens. This is best demonstrated in the performance of two songs: Mafo and Puta. In the video below, Naira Marley’s special brand of celebrity is revealed. Watch video below The post Watch Naira Marley Go Wild As He Performs ‘Mafo’ & ‘Pxta’ appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: NotJust okay